OL,3,CFourth person arrested in murder
OL,4,Cinvestigation after man dies in
OL,5,CKenilworth
OL,7,FA fourth person has been arrested as
OL,8,Fpart of a murder investigation into
OL,9,Fthe death of a man inside a house in
OL,10,FKenilworth.
OL,12,FPolice were called to the house on
OL,13,FChesnut Avenue just before midnight on
OL,14,FFriday night after concerns were
OL,15,Fraised for the welfare of a man.
OL,17,FThe man in his 40s died shortly
OL,18,Fafterwards.
