CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1774293066
OL,3,CFourth person arrested in murder
OL,4,Cinvestigation after man dies in
OL,5,CKenilworth
OL,7,F"We have arrested three people who
OL,8,Fwill be questioned to help us get a
OL,9,Ffull picture of what happened.
OL,10,FSpecially trained officers are
OL,11,Fsupporting the victim's family.
OL,13,F"At this time, we believe the incident
OL,14,Fwas contained to the house and there
OL,15,Fis no risk to the wider public.
OL,17,F"I know this will cause a great deal
OL,18,Fof shock in the local community. We'll
OL,19,Fhave officers in the area and I'd
OL,20,Fencourage anyone with information to
OL,21,Fspeak to one of them."
